                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460615-name-239" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460615-name-239" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460615-name-239" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460615-name-239" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a carpenter and live in Bermondsey-street, South<lb></lb>wark—the prisoner was my journeyman—I authorized him to sell chairs for me—if he sold them and obtained this money, he never paid it to me—he ought to have paid it the same night.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
