                        <interp inst="t18460615-name-240" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SMITH</persName>
                  </hi> Jun. I went with the prisoner to sell my father's chairs, to Mr. Jackson's—the prisoner went in with the chairs—he came out again, and told me I was to call at four o'clock for the money—when I called at that time he had had the money.</p>
